------------------------
PURPOSE
------------------------
This is a game to play hangman however, the program will cheat and does not actually choose a word until the user selects a letter.  
The user will be prmopted for a word length and if you enter a negative number, 
the program will reveal to you the possible words.

----------------------
Command Line Arguments
----------------------

Usage: python3 hangman.py

-----------------------
Running the program
---------------------

$ python3 hanman.py

--------------------
Dependencies
--------------------

There is a file with a list of words that must be in the same folder titled:

hangman_words.txt

